column10: There are two clusters of speeding and driving on the wrong side of the road on Hunt Club Rd.  One is from commuters seeking to avoid the light at Wiehle and Baron Cameron and cutting thru and speeding.  The other is Lake Fairfax related.; habitual speeding of cars coming and going to Lake Fairfax Dr and Lake Fairfax Park.  On-going hazzard and especially when school in session as cars go around Ring Rd and up North Shore where the school cross walk is ALWAYS ignored by most cars.
